    <ThingDef Name="MG_15_GA" ParentName="BaseMakeableGun_GA">
        <defName>Gun_MG_15_GA</defName>
        <label>MG 15</label>
        <description>Battlefield usage of the weapon was significant, but not to the extent of the Maxim weapons. The Bergmann MG 15 was an important weapon in that it filled a gap in the German armory between the rifle and the heavy machine gun. The only other light machine gun the Imperial German Army fielded before the Bergmann was adopted were the various Madsen light machine guns.</description>
